    <p>Find­ing the right mat­tress to suit your pref­er­ence can be over­whelm­ing, thanks to the va­ri­ety avail­able. Whether you pre­fer a medium, firm or ex­tra firm sleep­ing sur­face, you will find your ideal choice at your near­est Sea Horse store. Founded in</p>
    <p>1987 in Hong Kong, this bed­ding re­tailer has estab­lished it­self as a qual­ity bed­ding brand of­fer­ing rea­son­ably priced prod­ucts. In fact, its mat­tresses and pil­lows are used in five-star ho­tels and univer­sity dor­mi­to­ries. One of its best-sell­ing mod­els is Sea Horse Mat­tress (la­tex-like grade) with char­coal bam­boo fab­ric, de­signed to of­fer com­fort­able sup­port to the body plus a nat­u­ral re­sis­tance to mildew and dust mites.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at Sea Horse stores and on­line at Lazada, visit www.sea­horse­mat­tress.com/en for more in­for­ma­tion.</p>

